yees that perform transmission functions and those that perform marketing functions may request the use of company vehicles for local travel x about usexelonpepco holdings mergerleadershipcorporate governancecorporate citizenship and social responsibilityferc standards of conductshare ownership guidelinesour companiesdo business with pepco holdingscareerscommunity commitmentimproving reliabilityprotect the environmentuse advanced technologiessupporting renewable energybe a good community partnersafety programsustainability and corporate citizenship reportnewsroompress releasesmedia professionalsspeakers bureauconnect with uscareersmedia relationsour companies   exelon corporation  sitemapprivacy policy and terms of use      exelon corporation exchange nyse us dollar price unavailable change unavailable volume unavailable investor relations careersenergy suppliersvendors as public concern about ecosystems changing habitats pollution and land management continues to grow we remain committed to sustainable conservation and restoration initiatives as an integral part of our business operations learn more pom stock quote  pepco holdings llc  bloomberg markets error could not add to watchlist x  watchlist pepco holdings llc pomus acquired pomus was acquired by excus usd volume  before its here its on the bloomberg terminal learn more volume  current pe ratio ttm  earnings per share usd ttm  market cap usd  shares outstanding m  pricesales ttm  dividend indicated gross yield  sector utilities  price change  industry utilities  price change  related videos there are currently no related videos for this ticker please check back later company news press releases there are currently no news stories for this ticker please check back later there are currently no press releases for this ticker please check back later profile pepco holdings llc operates as a holding company the company through its subsidiaries generates distributes transmits and supplies electricity and natural ga